@rem *******************************************************************
@node "Examples" "Sample Applications"
@rem *******************************************************************
@prev "History"
Now after all you might ask the question:

@{JCENTER}@{b}@{fg fill}What can I use it for?@{fg text}@{ub}

@{JLEFT}Let me help your phantasy and I'm shure you will find some more
usefull applications for it.

@{LINDENT 7}@{PARI -2}

* Show your age in seconds (well that's obvious!)

* Show the number of seconds till the end of the millenium
(BIRTHDATE=1-1-2001, BIRTHTIME=00:00:00)

* Let others count days!  You know every time how many seconds are left on
your civil/military service.

* Enter a fortune teller's forcast of your death as BIRTHDATE and you can
see the seconds of your live dripping away :-))

* Use 1-1-0001 as date and you will see Jesus' age in seconds.

@{LINDENT 0}@{PARI -0}

The folder "Example Icons" contains some icons set up for this
applications. The program does not yet support project icons (Sorry).
That means you have to create a link from the program to the icon name to
use it.

@endnode
